.TH TRANSCRIBE 1 "February 2025" "dictee 0.3.2" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
transcribe \- transcribe audio files using NVIDIA Parakeet TDT
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B transcribe
.I audio.wav
.RI [ model_dir ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B transcribe
converts speech in audio files to text using the NVIDIA Parakeet TDT model.
Supports 25 languages with automatic language detection.
.PP
Audio should be 16kHz mono WAV format for best results.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.I audio.wav
Path to the audio file to transcribe (required)
.TP
.I model_dir
Path to TDT model directory (default: /usr/share/dictee/tdt)
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Transcribe a file:
.B transcribe recording.wav
.TP
Use custom model path:
.B transcribe recording.wav /path/to/tdt
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR transcribe-daemon (1),
.BR transcribe-client (1),
.BR transcribe-diarize (1),
.BR dictee (1)
